<view class="hero">
  <view class="eyebrow">欢迎来到学习小站</view>
  <view class="hero-title">先完成登录绑定</view>
</view>
<view class="section">
  <view class="card login-card">
    <view class="mascot">🐣</view>
    <view class="title">开启今天的学习</view>
    <view class="sub">绑定手机号后，可以同步学习记录、小挑战结果和老师反馈。</view>
    <button class="button" open-type="getPhoneNumber" bindtap="beginPhoneAuth" bindgetphonenumber="bindPhone" loading="{{phoneAuthOpening || binding}}" disabled="{{phoneAuthOpening || binding}}">绑定手机号并登录</button>
    <button class="button light" bindtap="login" disabled="{{phoneAuthOpening || binding}}">暂不绑定，先进入</button>
    <view class="login-tip">手机号可自动匹配已有课程权限；未开通课程也可以先登录。</view>
  </view>
</view>
<view class="section">
  <view class="bubble">账号被停用或暂未开通学习星球时，请联系老师或管理员处理。</view>
</view>
